menu "PixelPet"

    config PIXELPET_TIME_SCALE
        int "Game-time scale factor"
        range 1 3600
        default 360
        help
            Multiplier between real seconds and game seconds. With the
            default of 360, ten real seconds equals about one game hour
            so the full life cycle is observable in an afternoon. Set to
            1 for "real-time" play (one game day = one real day).

endmenu
